les, partagent de nombreuses caractéristiques et malgré toute leur complexité, nombre de leurs comportements sont fondamentalement simples.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 7aSCIENCE / Physics / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2023 Part 2z978311117804208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Physics, Chemistry, Mat.Sc, Geosc 2023z9783111318660oZDB-23-DPC40uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-3051-040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759830510423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759830510/original  a978-3-11-117804-2  DG Plus PP Package 2023 Part 2b2023  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DPCb2023